message.body: Did I not say that I was going to the hospital? Steph's dad has possible kidney failure... every hospital trip gets worse and worse. On top of caring for a father she worked 2 jobs today and this is the #### we come home too?
I bet you would never leave eden's home looking messy like that
And understanding you had your thesis is no excuse to not work
Right... you're out... that thing you "don't do" anymore.. whatever
Kiara bought me the ticket for my birthday
But you're still "out"... according to you, you don't go out anymore
